<div class='m1 module'>
<nav class='breadcrumb m4 show-lg'>Watch&nbsp;&nbsp;&rsaquo;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="breadcrumb__link" href="/watch/topics" rel=" up">Topics</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&rsaquo;&nbsp;&nbsp;</nav>

<h1 class='h1 h1--alt m2'>
Robots
</h1>

</div>

<div class='row'>
<div class='col col-lg-sidebarred'>
<!-- PB:B: copy --><div class='p2'>
<p>As machines grow ever more intelligent, they're emerging not just as powerful tools, but close companions. These TED Talks offer both whizzy demos and serious ideas on our evolving relationship with robots.</p>

</div>



<!-- PB:B: dynamic -->
<div class='section section--minor'>
<!--[if lte IE 8]>
<style>
